and will become overdue tomorrow.]

314
00:16:37,910 --> 00:16:38,710
What's wrong?

315
00:16:41,320 --> 00:16:42,240
Nothing.

316
00:16:43,120 --> 00:16:43,720
By the way,

317
00:16:44,000 --> 00:16:45,870
this hotel offers a complimentary

318
00:16:45,870 --> 00:16:47,550
Desert Rose Essential Oil Spa.

319
00:16:47,550 --> 00:16:48,590
I heard it's really good.

320
00:16:48,590 --> 00:16:49,680
I'd like to try it.

321
00:16:49,710 --> 00:16:51,950
The hotel service is that good?

322
00:16:51,600 --> 00:16:52,010
[On behalf of everyone at Svelto Hotel,]

323
00:16:52,010 --> 00:16:52,210
[we wish you a happy 10th anniversary!]

324
00:16:52,560 --> 00:16:54,710
Desert hot springs
are a Middle Eastern specialty.

325
00:16:54,710 --> 00:16:55,910
Worth giving it a try.

326
00:17:16,450 --> 00:17:17,819
[Pay Now]

327
00:17:19,950 --> 00:17:21,420
[Payment Successful]

328
00:17:32,130 --> 00:17:34,050
Honey, I'm back.

329
00:17:36,680 --> 00:17:37,550
Honey.

330
00:17:39,360 --> 00:17:40,560
Where are you?

331
00:17:43,570 --> 00:17:45,330
-Just do as I say.
-Honey.

332
00:17:45,830 --> 00:17:47,780
Why can't you understand what I'm saying?

333
00:17:47,780 --> 00:17:48,440
Hanging up.

334
00:17:51,550 --> 00:17:52,640
Minghui.

335
00:17:53,580 --> 00:17:55,240
Can't even handle a simple task.

336
00:17:55,240 --> 00:17:56,320
So indecisive.

337
00:17:59,250 --> 00:18:01,440
Did you call for turndown service?

338
00:18:01,460 --> 00:18:03,550
Yes, I called for turndown service.

339
00:18:03,640 --> 00:18:04,840
I was waiting for you.

340
00:18:10,730 --> 00:18:11,790
Who is it this time?

341
00:18:12,060 --> 00:18:13,830
It doesn't matter who it is today.

342
00:18:13,830 --> 00:18:15,690
You're the most important today.

343
00:18:34,410 --> 00:18:35,100
Wait a second.

344
00:18:35,100 --> 00:18:35,900
What's wrong?

345
00:18:35,950 --> 00:18:37,440
Something's caught in my hair.

346
00:18:37,440 --> 00:18:38,350
What is it?

347
00:18:39,880 --> 00:18:40,790
Let me see.

348
00:18:42,640 --> 00:18:43,440
What's wrong?

349
00:18:45,240 --> 00:18:46,270
What is this?

350
00:18:47,790 --> 00:18:50,030
Honey, you prepared this for me?

351
00:18:50,030 --> 00:18:51,270
This isn't mine.

352
00:18:51,690 --> 00:18:52,450
Not yours?

353
00:18:52,530 --> 00:18:53,350
Whose is this?

354
00:18:53,380 --> 00:18:54,590
How did it end up in your room?

355
00:18:54,590 --> 00:18:55,960
I have no idea.

356
00:18:55,960 --> 00:18:57,440
Did anyone come to the room
while I was away?

357
00:18:57,440 --> 00:18:58,880
Of course not.

358
00:18:58,920 --> 00:19:00,500
This room is newly checked in.

359
00:19:00,500 --> 00:19:02,100
Could it have been left
by the previous guest?

360
00:19:02,100 --> 00:19:03,400
The staff didn't clean properly.

361
00:19:03,400 --> 00:19:04,960
Didn't you notice during turndown service?

362
00:19:04,960 --> 00:19:06,030
The staff did the turndown service.

363
00:19:06,030 --> 00:19:07,590
I definitely didn't see it.

364
00:19:08,000 --> 00:19:08,920
No, I need to ask about this.

365
00:19:08,920 --> 00:19:09,440
No, don't.

366
00:19:09,440 --> 00:19:09,920
Call the staff.

367
00:19:09,920 --> 00:19:10,880
Just throw it away.

368
00:19:10,880 --> 00:19:12,150
No need to make a big deal out of it.

369
00:19:12,150 --> 00:19:13,610
This is not a small matter.

370
00:19:16,850 --> 00:19:18,980
Get a housekeeper to my room right now.

371
00:19:25,930 --> 00:19:26,780
Madam.

372
00:19:27,550 --> 00:19:28,810
I personally inspected this room

373
00:19:28,810 --> 00:19:30,290
after it was cleaned.

374
00:19:30,320 --> 00:19:32,330
And I'm sure it was not our staff's fault.

375
00:19:32,330 --> 00:19:33,710
So you think it's our fault?

376
00:19:33,710 --> 00:19:34,830
That's not what I meant.

377
00:19:34,830 --> 00:19:36,880
I wonder if you can double-check

378
00:19:36,880 --> 00:19:38,880
to see if it's something of your own.

379
00:19:39,420 --> 00:19:41,020
I'm certain this isn't mine.

380
00:19:41,200 --> 00:19:42,690
Let's just accept our bad luck.

381
00:19:42,690 --> 00:19:44,000
Have them throw it away.

382
00:19:44,000 --> 00:19:45,100
We can just change rooms.

383
00:19:45,100 --> 00:19:47,030
In a prestigious five-star hotel,

384
00:19:47,310 --> 00:19:48,790
a mysterious pair of underwear

385
00:19:48,790 --> 00:19:50,510
just appeared on our bed.

386
00:19:50,510 --> 00:19:52,310
Don't you find that disturbing?

387
00:19:58,210 --> 00:19:59,390
[Natalie]

388
00:19:59,720 --> 00:20:00,760
Natalie.

389
00:20:00,880 --> 00:20:03,030
I'm not here trying to blame anybody.

390
00:20:03,160 --> 00:20:05,070
We just want reassurance.

391
00:20:05,140 --> 00:20:07,470
I'm sure you're a competent housekeeper.

392
00:20:07,830 --> 00:20:09,760
But please do think carefully.

393
00:20:09,790 --> 00:20:10,880
During your cleaning and turndown service,

394
00:20:10,880 --> 00:20:12,260
did you

395
00:20:12,290 --> 00:20:15,960
notice this underwear at any point?

396
00:20:21,040 --> 00:20:21,730
Madam.

397
00:20:22,200 --> 00:20:23,560
Actually, this pair of underwear—

398
00:20:23,560 --> 00:20:24,680
Stop talking to her.

399
00:20:24,680 --> 00:20:25,940
She won't admit it.

400
00:20:25,970 --> 00:20:27,300
Why do you keep stopping me?

401
00:20:27,300 --> 00:20:28,580
I'm not stopping you.

402
00:20:28,950 --> 00:20:30,140
I mean

403
00:20:30,200 --> 00:20:31,310
let's call the general manager here

404
00:20:31,310 --> 00:20:32,310
to handle this matter.

405
00:20:32,310 --> 00:20:33,310
What do you think?

406
00:20:49,210 --> 00:20:50,140
Housekeeping.

407
00:20:53,300 --> 00:20:54,030
Mr. Ji.

408
00:20:54,050 --> 00:20:55,850
I have really checked this room.

409
00:20:59,230 --> 00:20:59,830
Mr. Nie,

410
00:20:59,830 --> 00:21:00,510
Mrs. Nie.

411
00:21:01,640 --> 00:21:02,790
I sincerely apologize.

412
00:21:02,790 --> 00:21:04,510
This is our oversight.

413
00:21:04,580 --> 00:21:06,790
It was caused by careless cleaning
by our staff.

414
00:21:06,790 --> 00:21:09,410
We will definitely
address this matter seriously.

415
00:21:09,410 --> 00:21:10,130
Natalie,

416
00:21:10,350 --> 00:21:11,910
you are no longer a housekeeper.

417
00:21:11,910 --> 00:21:14,160
-Mr. Ji, it's not my fault.
-Stop.

418
00:21:16,560 --> 00:21:17,420
Mr. Nie.

419
00:21:17,560 --> 00:21:19,100
Due to our inadequate service,

420
00:21:19,100 --> 00:21:20,950
we've caused you both
an unpleasant experience,

421
00:21:20,950 --> 00:21:23,450
especially
on your 10th wedding anniversary,

422
00:21:23,450 --> 00:21:24,650
such an important day,

423
00:21:24,650 --> 00:21:25,790
ruining your celebration.

424
00:21:25,790 --> 00:21:26,920
On behalf of the hotel,

425
00:21:26,920 --> 00:21:29,290
I sincerely apologize to you both again.

426
00:21:29,930 --> 00:21:30,590
Actually, all we need

427
00:21:30,590 --> 00:21:32,020
is an appropriate response.

428
00:21:32,020 --> 00:21:32,820
I understand.

429
00:21:33,010 --> 00:21:34,290
Our response

430
00:21:34,400 --> 00:21:36,570
is a sincere apology and compensation.

431
00:21:36,570 --> 00:21:38,330
I hope Mr. and Mrs. Nie

432
00:21:38,350 --> 00:21:40,030
will give us a chance to make it right.

433
00:21:40,030 --> 00:21:40,720
I wonder if you two

434
00:21:40,720 --> 00:21:43,000
are interested
in our desert tour activities.

435
00:21:43,000 --> 00:21:44,440
Such as falconry

436
00:21:44,440 --> 00:21:45,360
and dune bashing.

437
00:21:45,360 --> 00:21:46,960
We would be delighted to offer

438
00:21:46,960 --> 00:21:48,510
any premium experience activities

439
00:21:48,510 --> 00:21:50,180
to express our sincere apologies.

440
00:21:50,180 --> 00:21:51,580
That won't be necessary.

441
00:21:52,070 --> 00:21:52,830
Mr. Ji.

442
00:21:53,110 --> 00:21:54,640
We appreciate your sincerity.

443
00:21:54,640 --> 00:21:55,070
Yes.

444
00:21:55,070 --> 00:21:57,480
Actually, we don't want
to make things difficult for anyone.

445
00:21:57,480 --> 00:21:59,730
No guest
wants to encounter such situations.

446
00:21:59,730 --> 00:22:01,490
But since it happened,

447
00:22:01,560 --> 00:22:02,750
someone has to take responsibility, right?

448
00:22:02,750 --> 00:22:03,240
Yes.

449
00:22:04,130 --> 00:22:06,230
Didn't you say
you wanted to go dune bashing?

450
00:22:06,230 --> 00:22:07,490
I don't have any work tomorrow.

451
00:22:07,490 --> 00:22:08,420
I'll go with you.

452
00:22:10,680 --> 00:22:11,540
Thank you then.

453
00:22:12,680 --> 00:22:13,340
Excellent.

454
00:22:14,030 --> 00:22:14,640
Mr. Nie.

455
00:22:14,640 --> 00:22:15,650
This is my business card.

456
00:22:15,650 --> 00:22:17,090
It has my contact information.

457
00:22:15,940 --> 00:22:18,350
[Svelto Hotel Group] [Kenny Ji]
[Hotel Manager]

458
00:22:17,350 --> 00:22:18,510
I'll personally arrange

459
00:22:18,510 --> 00:22:19,750
your upcoming itinerary.

460
00:22:19,750 --> 00:22:21,200
Nice to meet you, Mr. Ji.

461
00:22:21,480 --> 00:22:22,510
Thank you for your help today.

462
00:22:22,510 --> 00:22:23,240
Please wait a moment.

463
00:22:23,240 --> 00:22:23,740
Sure.

464
00:22:30,690 --> 00:22:32,140
We should talk privately sometime.

465
00:22:32,060 --> 00:22:33,620
[Changyang Travel]

466
00:22:32,190 --> 00:22:33,950
It's a great pleasure to meet you,

467
00:22:33,950 --> 00:22:34,750
[Nie Yucheng]

468
00:22:34,040 --> 00:22:35,030
Director Nie.

469
00:22:35,700 --> 00:22:36,950
It's getting late.

470
00:22:37,000 --> 00:22:37,690
I won't disturb you both.

471
00:22:37,690 --> 00:22:38,890
Please get some rest.

472
00:22:42,610 --> 00:22:43,530
Wait.

473
00:22:45,440 --> 00:22:46,240
Yes, Mrs. Nie?

474
00:22:46,510 --> 00:22:47,580
Mr. Ji.

475
00:22:47,610 --> 00:22:49,400
Our complaint

476
00:22:49,720 --> 00:22:51,370
isn't directed at any individual.

477
00:22:51,370 --> 00:22:52,200
We're just fighting for

478
00:22:52,200 --> 00:22:54,110
the respect and rights we deserve.

479
00:22:54,110 --> 00:22:54,880
So,

480
00:22:54,880 --> 00:22:57,000
please show some mercy, Mr. Ji.

481
00:22:57,240 --> 00:22:57,810
All right.

482
00:22:57,810 --> 00:23:00,000
Mr. Ji knows how to handle this.

483
00:23:03,050 --> 00:23:03,800
I understand.

484
00:23:03,800 --> 00:23:04,680
Good night to you both.

485
00:23:04,680 --> 00:23:05,340
Good night.

486
00:23:12,150 --> 00:23:15,080
Mrs. Nie will find out the truth
sooner or later.

487
00:23:18,670 --> 00:23:20,400
That's not our job.

488
00:23:20,430 --> 00:23:21,500
We're here to serve,

489
00:23:21,500 --> 00:23:23,060
not to judge.

490
00:23:25,510 --> 00:23:26,350
Natalie,

491
00:23:26,370 --> 00:23:29,290
you and Tasha
are gonna swap shifts this week.

492
00:23:29,320 --> 00:23:31,720
Does that mean
I can still be a housekeeper?

493
00:23:31,720 --> 00:23:32,780
The case is closed.

494
00:23:33,270 --> 00:23:34,950
No need to dwell on it.

495
00:23:35,400 --> 00:23:36,730
Just focus on your work.

496
00:23:39,720 --> 00:23:42,320
I know
that Mr. Ji is fully aware of everything.

497
00:23:42,410 --> 00:23:42,950
Let's go.

498
00:24:52,960 --> 00:24:53,550
Good morning, Mrs. Nie.

499
00:24:53,550 --> 00:24:54,480
Good morning, Mr. Ji.

500
00:24:54,480 --> 00:24:55,910
How can I help you?

501
00:24:56,030 --> 00:24:56,590
About last night,

502
00:24:56,590 --> 00:24:57,440
I'm sorry

503
00:24:57,440 --> 00:24:59,120
for bothering you so late.

504
00:24:59,270 --> 00:25:01,070
No need to be so polite, Mrs. Nie.

505
00:25:03,120 --> 00:25:03,880
Mr. Ji,

506
00:25:03,880 --> 00:25:05,030
you know about my husband

507
00:25:05,030 --> 00:25:06,610
and the travel agency
where he works, right?

508
00:25:06,610 --> 00:25:07,240
Of course.

509
00:25:07,350 --> 00:25:09,610
I've heard a lot about Changyang Travel.

510
00:25:10,000 --> 00:25:10,640
Mr. Ji,

511
00:25:10,640 --> 00:25:12,990
are you interested
in domestic travel packages?

512
00:25:12,990 --> 00:25:14,830
I know my husband is currently

513
00:25:14,830 --> 00:25:17,310
exploring some
international luxury wilderness routes

514
00:25:17,310 --> 00:25:19,000
and inspecting some international hotels.

515
00:25:19,000 --> 00:25:20,480
If you're interested,

516
00:25:20,480 --> 00:25:22,160
I can have him contact you.

517
00:25:22,160 --> 00:25:23,110
You two could have a good chat.

518
00:25:23,110 --> 00:25:25,440
Thank you for the introduction, Mrs. Nie.

519
00:25:27,480 --> 00:25:28,640
Have you had breakfast, Mr. Ji?

520
00:25:28,640 --> 00:25:31,110
Would you like to get something
to eat together?

521
00:25:31,110 --> 00:25:32,110
Mrs. Nie,

522
00:25:32,150 --> 00:25:33,070
what do you want?

523
00:25:33,070 --> 00:25:34,270
Just say it directly.

524
00:25:34,310 --> 00:25:37,710
I'd like to check the surveillance footage
outside our room.

525
00:25:40,960 --> 00:25:42,210
I'm sorry, Mrs. Nie.

526
00:25:42,350 --> 00:25:43,550
The hotel has a policy

527
00:25:43,720 --> 00:25:45,700
that surveillance footage
is not available to guests.

528
00:25:45,700 --> 00:25:47,300
Can't you make an exception?

529
00:25:48,160 --> 00:25:49,480
I truly apologize.

530
00:25:50,750 --> 00:25:51,510
However, regarding this matter,

531
00:25:51,510 --> 00:25:53,200
we've already completed our investigation.

532
00:25:53,200 --> 00:25:53,940
What's the conclusion?

533
00:25:53,940 --> 00:25:56,550
It's entirely our hotel's responsibility,

534
00:25:56,590 --> 00:25:58,450
so you can rest assured, Mrs. Nie.

535
00:26:02,940 --> 00:26:04,110
Please don't misunderstand, Mr. Ji.

536
00:26:04,110 --> 00:26:06,960
Actually, I don't really care about
seeing the footage.

537
00:26:06,960 --> 00:26:08,560
I'm not the suspicious type.

538
00:26:08,560 --> 00:26:10,310
I trust my husband completely.

539
00:26:10,830 --> 00:26:13,030
You share a rock-solid relationship
with Mr. Nie.

540
00:26:13,030 --> 00:26:14,070
This minor misunderstanding

541
00:26:14,070 --> 00:26:16,550
can be considered as adding

542
00:26:16,550 --> 00:26:18,550
a little spice to your anniversary.

543
00:26:18,790 --> 00:26:20,720
We feel deeply apologetic

544
00:26:20,720 --> 00:26:22,780
and don't know how to make it up to you.

545
00:26:22,790 --> 00:26:24,270
Mr. Ji, please don't blame yourself.

546
00:26:24,270 --> 00:26:26,030
You manage such a large hotel

547
00:26:26,110 --> 00:26:27,110
and still personally attend

548
00:26:27,110 --> 00:26:28,270
to our small matters.

549
00:26:28,270 --> 00:26:29,400
We're already very grateful.

550
00:26:29,400 --> 00:26:30,000
Not at all.

551
00:26:30,070 --> 00:26:32,070
No service matter
is too small for a hotel.

552
00:26:32,070 --> 00:26:33,000
So, Mrs. Nie,

553
00:26:33,000 --> 00:26:34,920
is there anything else
I can help you with?

554
00:26:34,920 --> 00:26:35,920
No, thank you.

555
00:26:54,270 --> 00:26:54,880
Good.

556
00:26:56,070 --> 00:26:56,680
Mr. Ji.

557
00:26:58,440 --> 00:27:00,460
Thank you for your hospitality these days.

558
00:27:00,460 --> 00:27:02,100
My wife and I have had
a very pleasant stay.

559
00:27:02,100 --> 00:27:03,700
Not at all. It's my pleasure.

560
00:27:06,880 --> 00:27:07,480
By the way,

561
00:27:08,010 --> 00:27:10,350
the experience these past 2 days
has been excellent.

562
00:27:10,350 --> 00:27:11,750
It's definitely worth the trip.

563
00:27:11,750 --> 00:27:13,590
I hope your company's travel routes

564
00:27:13,590 --> 00:27:14,790
can be finalized soon.

565
00:27:14,790 --> 00:27:15,590
We're really looking forward to

566
00:27:15,590 --> 00:27:17,560
working with a leading enterprise
like Changyang.

567
00:27:17,560 --> 00:27:18,920
If you need anything,

568
00:27:18,950 --> 00:27:19,920
feel free to contact me anytime.

569
00:27:19,920 --> 00:27:20,870
Absolutely.

570
00:27:20,890 --> 00:27:21,600
How about this?

571
00:27:21,600 --> 00:27:23,680
After I get back, we'll connect

572
00:27:23,700 --> 00:27:25,080
and finalize the specific routes.

573
00:27:25,080 --> 00:27:25,660
No problem.

574
00:27:25,660 --> 00:27:26,290
Good.

575
00:27:26,680 --> 00:27:27,400
We'll be in touch.

576
00:27:27,400 --> 00:27:28,060
Thank you.

577
00:27:28,090 --> 00:27:28,590
Thanks.

578
00:27:28,590 --> 00:27:28,960
Let me see you out.

579
00:27:28,960 --> 00:27:29,510
Okay.

580
00:27:40,830 --> 00:27:41,480
Mr. Nie,

581
00:27:41,710 --> 00:27:42,440
have a safe journey.

582
00:27:42,440 --> 00:27:43,040
Thank you.

583
00:27:43,240 --> 00:27:43,770
Bye-bye.

584
00:27:45,190 --> 00:27:46,130
Let's go.

585
00:27:51,330 --> 00:27:51,860
Bye-bye.

586
00:27:52,990 --> 00:27:54,510
[Svelto Hotel Group]

587
00:28:01,540 --> 00:28:09,650
[Svelto Hotel Group]

588
00:28:05,960 --> 00:28:06,720
Stephen,

589
00:28:07,290 --> 00:28:09,610
you've been calling me
quite frequently lately.

590
00:28:09,610 --> 00:28:12,130
Mr. Ji, this offer is very special.

591
00:28:12,590 --> 00:28:13,440
You know what?

592
00:28:14,200 --> 00:28:15,720
By the 13th of next month,

593
00:28:16,510 --> 00:28:17,920
I'll have been working abroad

594
00:28:17,920 --> 00:28:19,510
for exactly 10 years.

595
00:28:20,160 --> 00:28:22,070
I'm about to be promoted
to general manager,

596
00:28:22,070 --> 00:28:23,750
so I won't be changing jobs.

597
00:28:27,170 --> 00:28:35,080
[Svelto Hotel Group]

598
00:28:37,560 --> 00:28:41,840
[Shanghai, China]

599
00:28:49,690 --> 00:28:51,230
These are really heavy.

600
00:28:52,970 --> 00:28:54,050
Finally home.

601
00:28:54,110 --> 00:28:58,000
-Low battery. Please replace.
-When I wake up,

602
00:28:58,000 --> 00:29:01,480
Mom teaches me English.

603
00:29:13,070 --> 00:29:13,720
Sister,

604
00:29:14,160 --> 00:29:16,110
did we come at a bad time?

605
00:29:18,830 --> 00:29:20,070
It's fine.

606
00:29:20,750 --> 00:29:21,890
These two

607
00:29:21,910 --> 00:29:23,260
are my younger sister

608
00:29:23,290 --> 00:29:25,100
and her husband.

609
00:29:25,640 --> 00:29:27,750
They just returned from vacation abroad

610
00:29:27,750 --> 00:29:29,570
and are stopping by my place to rest.

611
00:29:29,570 --> 00:29:31,960
You two can go rest in the bedroom.

612
00:29:31,990 --> 00:29:34,230
We'll be finished here soon.

613
00:29:35,960 --> 00:29:36,480
Okay.

614
00:29:38,480 --> 00:29:40,090
Sorry.

615
00:29:40,140 --> 00:29:41,170
It's alright.

616
00:29:41,190 --> 00:29:42,160
Let's continue.

617
00:29:42,820 --> 00:29:47,690
My father teaches me tennis
every afternoon.

618
00:29:47,720 --> 00:29:49,000
Let's go. Let's go.

619
00:29:49,030 --> 00:29:51,920
-My hobby is reading...
-Let's go.

620
00:29:52,310 --> 00:29:53,370
Swimming

621
00:29:53,680 --> 00:29:54,710
and programming.

622
00:29:55,440 --> 00:29:56,780
I believe

623
00:29:56,800 --> 00:30:02,350
reading is how I connect with the world.

624
00:30:04,640 --> 00:30:05,960
Man is so funny.

625
00:30:06,430 --> 00:30:07,880
Don't talk to me right now.

626
00:30:07,880 --> 00:30:09,000
I'm angry now.

627
00:30:09,740 --> 00:30:11,970
I know you don't want to deal with them.

628
00:30:14,210 --> 00:30:15,520
What happened to your hand?

629
00:30:15,520 --> 00:30:16,930
I was so annoyed with them.

630
00:30:16,930 --> 00:30:20,260
I wasn't paying attention
and got my hand caught in the door.

631
00:30:21,010 --> 00:30:22,720
They just invite themselves over

632
00:30:22,720 --> 00:30:24,520
and have been here so many times.

633
00:30:25,920 --> 00:30:26,610
This time,

634
00:30:26,630 --> 00:30:28,370
my sister really has a problem.

635
00:30:28,590 --> 00:30:29,830
She enrolled Man

636
00:30:29,830 --> 00:30:31,220
in an international school.

637
00:30:31,220 --> 00:30:33,420
They suddenly wanted to do a home visit.

638
00:30:33,840 --> 00:30:35,810
When she registered
at that international school,

639
00:30:35,810 --> 00:30:37,340
she put down our address...

640
00:30:41,530 --> 00:30:42,530
Just bear with it.

641
00:30:42,980 --> 00:30:43,620
She

642
00:30:44,110 --> 00:30:45,620
put down our home address.

643
00:30:45,740 --> 00:30:47,570
The teacher suddenly wanted to visit.

644
00:30:47,570 --> 00:30:49,230
She just needs to put on a show.

645
00:30:50,330 --> 00:30:52,930
But home visits
should be at their actual home.

646
00:30:53,430 --> 00:30:54,120
Fine.

647
00:30:54,150 --> 00:30:56,150
I understand putting on a show,

648
00:30:56,330 --> 00:30:57,710
but she could rent a place for that,

649
00:30:57,710 --> 00:30:58,680
couldn't she?

650
00:30:59,200 --> 00:31:00,130
I think

651
00:31:00,530 --> 00:31:02,410
your sister thinks
you're easy to take advantage of.

652
00:31:02,410 --> 00:31:04,160
She keeps fleecing the same sheep
over and over.

653
00:31:04,160 --> 00:31:05,090
And look at this,

654
00:31:05,220 --> 00:31:06,430
it's all a mess.

655
00:31:06,770 --> 00:31:09,350
Well, that's what happens
when I marry such a good husband.

656
00:31:09,350 --> 00:31:11,350
She's just jealous of me—

657
00:31:11,550 --> 00:31:13,660
jealous that I don't have to worry about
food or clothes

658
00:31:13,660 --> 00:31:15,500
and that you treat me so well.

659
00:31:16,830 --> 00:31:17,470
By the way,

660
00:31:17,790 --> 00:31:18,720
I'll make sure

661
00:31:18,890 --> 00:31:19,930
they leave soon.

662
00:31:20,050 --> 00:31:21,810
At most, I'll have them for dinner,

663
00:31:21,810 --> 00:31:24,340
but they'll definitely leave tonight,
okay?

664
00:31:24,790 --> 00:31:26,160
You should have

665
00:31:26,590 --> 00:31:28,030
at least told me about this,

666
00:31:28,030 --> 00:31:28,960
right?

667
00:31:29,030 --> 00:31:30,330
I'm sorry.

668
00:31:30,350 --> 00:31:31,350
I forgot.

669
00:31:34,190 --> 00:31:34,910
Wait.

670
00:31:36,060 --> 00:31:37,000
Is Yao Zhigang

671
00:31:37,000 --> 00:31:38,590
wearing my clothes?

672
00:31:39,010 --> 00:31:41,270
And is your sister wearing your clothes?

673
00:31:41,640 --> 00:31:42,880
Those are old clothes,

674
00:31:42,880 --> 00:31:44,720
and we hardly wear them anyway.

675
00:31:46,360 --> 00:31:46,950
Oh right,

676
00:31:47,510 --> 00:31:49,320
didn't I buy you a new suit jacket?

677
00:31:49,320 --> 00:31:50,920
Let me get it for you to try on.

678
00:31:53,990 --> 00:31:57,970
The new suit jacket I just bought for you.

679
00:31:58,640 --> 00:31:59,960
You should try it on.

680
00:32:00,880 --> 00:32:01,540
It's here.

681
00:32:01,870 --> 00:32:02,500
Come on.

682
00:32:03,650 --> 00:32:05,110
This suits you perfectly.

683
00:32:07,950 --> 00:32:08,490
Do I look good?

684
00:32:08,490 --> 00:32:09,250
So handsome.

685
00:32:09,960 --> 00:32:10,920
My husband

686
00:32:10,940 --> 00:32:12,000
is the most handsome,

687
00:32:12,000 --> 00:32:14,200
even more handsome than an Arab prince.

688
00:32:17,220 --> 00:32:19,080
Your home has such a great layout,

689
00:32:19,100 --> 00:32:20,960
and the decoration is so special.

690
00:32:21,270 --> 00:32:22,750
French country style.

691
00:32:23,170 --> 00:32:24,780
Take care.

692
00:32:32,670 --> 00:32:34,780
This situation

693
00:32:35,310 --> 00:32:36,770
is quite embarrassing.

694
00:32:37,050 --> 00:32:40,510
Mainly because the interview notice
came so suddenly.

695
00:32:40,540 --> 00:32:41,170
You know.

696
00:32:41,860 --> 00:32:42,720
Look at my sister.

697
00:32:42,720 --> 00:32:45,250
She is so quick-witted.

698
00:32:45,520 --> 00:32:47,720
It just left me speechless with fright.

699
00:32:47,850 --> 00:32:48,570
Uncle!

700
00:32:49,160 --> 00:32:50,790
Man. Man.

701
00:32:50,790 --> 00:32:51,790
Have you finished your homework?

702
00:32:51,790 --> 00:32:52,720
Yes.

703
00:32:52,720 --> 00:32:53,720
Is it correct?

704
00:32:56,000 --> 00:32:56,630
Yucheng.

705
00:32:56,790 --> 00:32:57,330
Have a seat.

706
00:32:57,330 --> 00:32:58,210
Let me have a word with you.

707
00:32:58,210 --> 00:32:59,610
Don't wrinkle your suit.

708
00:33:00,410 --> 00:33:01,210
What's wrong?

709
00:33:03,410 --> 00:33:04,540
Still no news yet?

710
00:33:05,160 --> 00:33:06,690
You need to try something new.

711
00:33:06,690 --> 00:33:07,560
The kid is right here.

712
00:33:07,560 --> 00:33:08,680
He doesn't understand.

713
00:33:08,680 --> 00:33:10,410
See how good I am to you.

714
00:33:13,560 --> 00:33:16,210
I found this specially for you.
It treats infertility.

715
00:33:16,210 --> 00:33:18,270
You can't rush these things, you know?

716
00:33:18,270 --> 00:33:19,400
With the right method,

717
00:33:19,400 --> 00:33:20,960
a little boost and you'll get results.

718
00:33:20,960 --> 00:33:22,220
Seven days is one course.

719
00:33:22,220 --> 00:33:23,110
Take it after meals.

720
00:33:23,110 --> 00:33:24,040
One packet a day.

721
00:33:24,070 --> 00:33:24,550
Got it?

722
00:33:24,550 --> 00:33:25,790
Okay, got it.

723
00:33:25,830 --> 00:33:26,790
I'll go check on Miyu

724
00:33:26,790 --> 00:33:27,720
-to see if she needs my help.
-You have to eat.

725
00:33:27,720 --> 00:33:29,120
Fine, just leave it here.

726
00:33:29,900 --> 00:33:31,560
It's really a secret formula.

727
00:33:34,200 --> 00:33:36,200
Congratulations to Kenny

728
00:33:36,220 --> 00:33:39,650
on winning the Svelto Hotel Group's

729
00:33:39,680 --> 00:33:42,960
Outstanding General Manager of the Year.

730
00:33:51,640 --> 00:33:53,100
Thank you so much.

731
00:33:55,160 --> 00:33:58,290
He's also the youngest manager

732
00:33:58,510 --> 00:34:00,510
in the history of the group.

733
00:34:01,000 --> 00:34:03,140
The most handsome one!

734
00:34:03,850 --> 00:34:06,340
He has earned himself

735
00:34:06,510 --> 00:34:09,550
a candidacy to be promoted

736
00:34:09,550 --> 00:34:10,840
from acting manager to general manager.

737
00:34:10,840 --> 00:34:13,770
Mr. Ji didn't get promoted
to general manager again?

738
00:34:15,840 --> 00:34:16,960
And the other candidate

739
00:34:16,960 --> 00:34:18,670
is Mr. Smith.

740
00:34:18,670 --> 00:34:21,480
Andy Smith is a specialist

741
00:34:21,480 --> 00:34:25,440
from the group.

742
00:34:25,440 --> 00:34:27,760
He's one of the best general managers
from our company.

743
00:34:27,760 --> 00:34:30,670
Please, let's welcome Mr. Smith.

744
00:34:32,360 --> 00:34:33,630
What nonsense is he talking about?

745
00:34:33,630 --> 00:34:35,989
Mr. Ji is the most suitable person
for the general manager position.

746
00:34:35,989 --> 00:34:36,780
Welcome.

747
00:34:39,480 --> 00:34:40,480
Mr. Smith.

748
00:34:42,150 --> 00:34:43,590
Just call me Andy, guys.

749
00:34:45,480 --> 00:34:47,780
I've got not so many rules
when you work with me.

750
00:34:47,780 --> 00:34:50,310
But the most important thing
is performance.

751
00:34:51,940 --> 00:34:53,400
It's a little harsh on you.

752
00:34:56,130 --> 00:34:57,410
No, thanks to you.

753
00:35:13,840 --> 00:35:14,710
Phil.

754
00:35:15,880 --> 00:35:17,320
I closed the deal,

755
00:35:17,960 --> 00:35:19,320
hit the KPI,

756
00:35:19,510 --> 00:35:21,640
and secured the Chinese partnership.

757
00:35:23,400 --> 00:35:25,180
You know better than anyone

758
00:35:25,590 --> 00:35:27,860
that you shouldn't push me out.

759
00:35:29,750 --> 00:35:30,940
Some doors

760
00:35:30,960 --> 00:35:32,110
stay closed from the beginning,

761
00:35:32,110 --> 00:35:33,640
regardless of the outcome.

762
00:35:34,110 --> 00:35:34,710
Still,

763
00:35:35,320 --> 00:35:37,520
I thought this time would be different.

764
00:35:37,650 --> 00:35:40,120
I thought you would recognize

765
00:35:40,150 --> 00:35:41,880
what I've brought to the table.

766
00:35:43,210 --> 00:35:45,000
Because you're very good.

767
00:35:46,250 --> 00:35:48,050
It's well-known in the company.

768
00:35:48,840 --> 00:35:50,110
This is a big group.

769
00:35:51,230 --> 00:35:54,880
We value your amazing innovatability.

770
00:35:55,190 --> 00:35:57,210
A young man like you

771
00:35:57,230 --> 00:35:58,420
is ambitious.

772
00:35:58,760 --> 00:36:02,420
Why are you concerned about
the title of general manager?

773
00:36:10,630 --> 00:36:13,880
Our next hotel is in South Africa.

774
00:36:38,070 --> 00:36:39,230
Sister, Zhigang,

775
00:36:39,230 --> 00:36:39,880
have some food.

776
00:36:39,880 --> 00:36:40,680
-Okay.
-Okay.

777
00:36:41,110 --> 00:36:41,760
Man, here.

778
00:36:41,760 --> 00:36:42,960
Try this salted egg yolk chicken wing.

779
00:36:42,960 --> 00:36:44,110
Thank you, Aunt.

780
00:36:44,550 --> 00:36:46,010
I'd like to toast Yucheng.

781
00:36:46,330 --> 00:36:47,120
Yucheng,

782
00:36:47,150 --> 00:36:49,210
you're the lucky star of our family

783
00:36:49,590 --> 00:36:51,980
and especially a benefactor
to our Zhigang.

784
00:36:51,980 --> 00:36:54,820
The job you arranged for Zhigang

785
00:36:55,880 --> 00:36:58,530
is really high pay for little work.

786
00:36:58,690 --> 00:37:00,730
Everyone's so jealous.

787
00:37:00,960 --> 00:37:02,080
I was like,

788
00:37:02,230 --> 00:37:04,460
"How could you compare with me?

789
00:37:04,490 --> 00:37:06,550
I have such a great brother-in-law."

790
00:37:07,760 --> 00:37:09,400
And this time,

791
00:37:09,420 --> 00:37:11,730
with Man's school application,

792
00:37:12,100 --> 00:37:13,830
we've troubled you again.

793
00:37:13,890 --> 00:37:15,570
But rest assured, Yucheng,

794
00:37:15,640 --> 00:37:17,710
it won't happen again.

795
00:37:17,840 --> 00:37:18,320
Here,

796
00:37:18,680 --> 00:37:19,820
a toast to you.

797
00:37:19,840 --> 00:37:21,110
We're one, no need for formalities.

798
00:37:21,110 --> 00:37:21,510
Good.

799
00:37:21,530 --> 00:37:22,790
Sorry for the trouble.

800
00:37:22,920 --> 00:37:24,070
It's nothing.

801
00:37:29,520 --> 00:37:30,850
This wine is delicious.

802
00:37:34,660 --> 00:37:35,370
Miyu.

803
00:37:35,480 --> 00:37:37,110
Did you bring back a lot of nice things

804
00:37:37,110 --> 00:37:39,110
from your trip abroad?

805
00:37:39,870 --> 00:37:42,210
I bought gifts for you guys, Mom, and Dad.

806
00:37:42,440 --> 00:37:43,470
You can take them back

807
00:37:43,470 --> 00:37:44,350
when you leave.

808
00:37:45,880 --> 00:37:47,360
What time is your train?

809
00:37:47,600 --> 00:37:48,910
No rush for the tickets.

810
00:37:48,910 --> 00:37:50,110
After we wake up tomorrow,

811
00:37:50,110 --> 00:37:50,670
we'll buy them.

812
00:37:50,670 --> 00:37:52,650
-High-speed trains run frequently.
-Yeah.

813
00:37:52,650 --> 00:37:53,190
Very convenient.

814
00:37:53,190 --> 00:37:53,790
Eat more.

815
00:37:57,840 --> 00:37:58,840
Sister, Zhigang,

816
00:37:58,870 --> 00:37:59,470
I'm sorry.

817
00:37:59,480 --> 00:38:00,550
I'm going on a business trip tomorrow.

818
00:38:00,550 --> 00:38:02,210
I still have unfinished work
at the company.

819
00:38:02,210 --> 00:38:04,170
I need to work overtime.
Please enjoy your meal.

820
00:38:04,170 --> 00:38:06,630
Didn't you just return
from a business trip?

821
00:38:06,960 --> 00:38:08,830
Their company just started a new project.

822
00:38:08,830 --> 00:38:10,050
He can't afford to delay.

823
00:38:10,050 --> 00:38:10,820
Go on and eat.

824
00:38:10,840 --> 00:38:12,040
I'll go help him pack.

825
00:38:12,850 --> 00:38:13,780
Man, here.

826
00:38:14,090 --> 00:38:15,080
Have another chicken wing.

827
00:38:15,080 --> 00:38:16,980
-Eat more.
-Thank you, Aunt.

828
00:38:18,360 --> 00:38:19,500
Is he really okay?

829
00:38:20,290 --> 00:38:20,890
It's fine.

830
00:38:22,110 --> 00:38:23,070
Go on and eat.

831
00:38:23,510 --> 00:38:24,050
Eat.

832
00:38:24,330 --> 00:38:25,320
Have some soup.

833
00:38:26,380 --> 00:38:28,110
I won't be coming home tonight.

834
00:38:29,170 --> 00:38:30,130
Why?

835
00:38:30,510 --> 00:38:31,840
I have a business trip tomorrow.

836
00:38:31,840 --> 00:38:33,280
There's still a lot to do at the office.

837
00:38:33,280 --> 00:38:34,950
I'll be working until late at night.

838
00:38:34,950 --> 00:38:37,400
I'll get a hotel room near the office.

839
00:38:37,420 --> 00:38:40,150
I need to catch an early flight
tomorrow morning.

840
00:38:41,070 --> 00:38:42,530
You're not angry, are you?

841
00:38:44,150 --> 00:38:45,150
No, of course not.

842
00:38:46,550 --> 00:38:48,800
Why would I be angry?

843
00:38:50,360 --> 00:38:51,320
The house is crowded.

844
00:38:51,320 --> 00:38:52,760
I'm worried you won't be comfortable.

845
00:38:52,760 --> 00:38:53,800
But...

846
00:38:54,100 --> 00:38:55,500
It's okay. It's nothing.

847
00:38:56,450 --> 00:38:57,320
Don't worry.

848
00:38:58,970 --> 00:38:59,700
I'm leaving.

849
00:39:01,100 --> 00:39:01,850
Take care.

850
00:39:13,790 --> 00:39:17,930
[JD Cinema Zone]

851
00:39:13,860 --> 00:39:14,630
Look.

852
00:39:14,890 --> 00:39:17,290
Their cinema zone is really nice.

853
00:39:17,320 --> 00:39:18,150
And it's free.

854
00:39:19,570 --> 00:39:20,930
Why hasn't Miyu come back yet?

855
00:39:20,930 --> 00:39:22,090
Is she mad at us?

856
00:39:22,180 --> 00:39:23,360
What would she be mad about?

857
00:39:23,360 --> 00:39:25,490
Miyu wouldn't dare to be angry with me.

858
00:39:25,960 --> 00:39:27,840
She's not my father's biological daughter.

859
00:39:27,840 --> 00:39:29,150
He's raised her ever since she was little.

860
00:39:29,150 --> 00:39:31,030
She can't please us enough.

